posting_body: ['CONTACT COREY for MORE INFO, PICS', 'TEXT CODE: SR22029089CN & your name to', 'show contact info', 'Or call or email me', "IF THIS PLACE DOESN'T FIT,", 'ASK ABOUT OUR EXTENSIVE LIST OF', 'OTHER PROPERTIES / RENT / BUY / SELL /', 'LUXURY ESTATES / HOUSES /', 'COMMERCIAL / APARTMENTS', "*and we'll assist you through the entire process!*", 'House For Rent 1 Year+', '$11,995 / Per Month', '6 Beds', '7 Baths', '2,338 SqFt', 'Situated behind prestigious gates, sits this this private hidden gem.', 'Country style home in Beverly Hills for Lease.', 'Private home with 6 bedrooms and 6 and a half bathrooms, including a large master suite with a fireplace, walk in closet and master bath.', 'The kitchen opens up to a charming eat in area with beamed ceilings as well as a large great room/family room with beautiful built ins, a large fireplace and lots of light.', 'There are also seperate maids quarters with a bath and a large bonus room with its own kitchenette and bath that can be used as guest quarters or as a cabana for the large pool and sauna.', 'This home is wonderful for entertaining, with two large garages (four cars), built in BBQ (outdoor and indoor) and beautiful gardens.', 'This is the quintessential California canyon home that features indoor/outdoor living at its best!', 'Please submit credit report & full application with offer.', 'Ready for immediate occupancy.', 'Home is located on property with other homes but does not have permission to access other parts of property.', 'Owner pays for pool maintenance and gardening.', 'Tennant is responsible for gas and electric.', '*** Text Code: SR22029089CN & your name to', 'show contact info', 'For Details & Photos***', 'And check out my website: <URL>/', 'Brought to you by Corey Trevor at Los Angeles Area - eXp Realty of California, Inc.', 'CA DRE#01878277 Listing Agent by Amy Ickovics  Keller Williams Encino-Sherman Oaks DRE#: 01811831']
